This release by IU perfectly explains why she is my favourite artist in the entirety of the Korean music industry She is the benchmark of what a true artist should be like If you are an avid Kpop fan it is a well known fact that idol tend to get replaced by newer and younger idol group and soon will be forgotten by the general public But what make IU still so well received and relevant to the general public all kill on all chart with every song despite being in the industry for nearly a decade I believe is due to her intelligence and strategy showcasing that she isn ’ t merely a product of the system that will be thrown away after her prime age or after several hit song Her fortitude in releasing controversial song like ‘ Zeze ’ proved to be a move by IU in exploring contentious theme which reinforced to me her innate quality a an artist Her music which explores theme like love Good day self empowerment palette criticism of the negative public obsession with a celebrity BbiBbi backed up with the quality instrumentals and music reminds u that IU is to be an artist taken seriously She isn ’ t here to just sing and be swept away by ‘ pretty faced ’ new idol She ha substance not fluff She is head and shoulder above the medium who ha criticised her in the past she is on her own league ahead of mere idol group who are product of their company manufactured to be well received by fan only to be thrown away once their quality of appearance fade away with age The group that have debuted or been active with IU from the start are nowhere a nearly well received by the public compared to IU Most of them are relic of a bygone era No hate to other group but when you see QUALITY there is bound to be a contrast that will be drawn And when there is a quality artist she will transcend time and generation and still be so well liked for her quality itself despite the passage of time And that is IU
